Business Brief -- Harsco Corp.:
   Firm Proposes to Buy Back
   Up to 15.2% of Common
The Harrisburg, Pa., company said the stock purchased in
the buy-back will be used for possible further acquisitions
and other general corporate purposes.
   Herzog, Heine, Geduld Inc. was appointed broker for the
repurchase.
   Harsco is a diversified industrial company that produces
products and services for defense, industrial, commercial and
construction markets.